half of that threshold energy.

00:04:02.800 --> 00:04:05.090
But you have three of them.

00:04:05.090 --> 00:04:10.864
So will an electron
is or is not ejected?

00:04:10.864 --> 00:04:11.572
AUDIENCE: Is not.

00:04:14.350 --> 00:04:16.000
CATHERINE DRENNAN: Is not.

