00:27:24.310 --> 00:27:27.940
And now, if we do
this calculation,

00:27:27.940 --> 00:27:31.360
so if we use Planck's
constant divided

00:27:31.360 --> 00:27:33.670
by the mass of the
electron-- and that's

00:27:33.670 --> 00:27:38.470
